    "body": "Storing internal transactions to leveldb is not something we'd want to include by default, since it will blow up disk requirements. Geth is not primarily aimed at specialized targets like block explorers, who indeed have different requirements and hardware budgets. This issue is not really a bug report, so I'll close this. ",
